ce--latency\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749449437\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent注入导致服务延迟增加，出现DeadlineExceeded和context deadline exceeded错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"日志显示adservice多个实例出现'Agent failed to start!'、'attempting to load Byteman agent more than once'，同时frontend服务报告'failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"由于adservice延迟问题导致的RPC调用超时，出现DeadlineExceeded错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend服务在多个节点上频繁出现'failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded'错误，表明无法从adservice获取广告数据\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析发现**：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：\n   - `frontend`服务频繁出现RPC调用超时错误（DeadlineExceeded）\n   - `adservice`出现Byteman agent注入相关的异常\n\n2. **故障链分析**：\n   - adservice的三个实例（adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2）都出现了Byteman agent启动失败的问题\n   - 这导致了adservice的延迟增加，具体表现为\"AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749449437\"规则被触发\n   - frontend服务在调用adservice获取广告时因此超时\n\n3. **关键证据**：\n   - Byteman agent相关错误出现频率高（共出现6次）\n   - frontend的RPC超时错误分布广泛，涉及所有frontend实例\n   - 时间上Byteman agent错误与RPC超时错误同时发生", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常高的响应时间 (rrt 和 rrt_max 显著增加)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt 从 3110.18 增加到 230562.82 (变化率 1.9468), rrt_max 从 42545.5 增加到 499861.0 (变化率 1.6862)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个 frontend Pod 的响应时间 (rrt 和 rrt_max) 显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: rrt 从 11576.52 增加到 56678.5 (变化率 1.3216), rrt_max 从 250739.0 增加到 615875.0 (变化率 0.8427); frontend-1: rrt 从 11804.52 增加到 56944.74 (变化率 1.3132), rrt_max 从 265